yTime":"2020-08-18T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"講出黎會舒服d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"人多好辦事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"無人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:37:32.000Z","msg":"總有解決辦法"},{"pid":"44f26fa3f699b9328d9ece2c43366b8435e23f35","tid":2163531,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T21:29:27.000Z","msg":"冷靜啲 有乜事埋嚟同我傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 之前讀書嗰陣壓力大得濟<br />\n研究咗好耐點死先舒服啲<br />\n最後發現得安樂死最舒服<br />\n其他死法都好撚痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁既然死都唔驚 仲有乜好怕<br />\n去到最壞嗰一刻 大不了咪死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec30370713e9d2bb8a50ff809ff2d23ef9540ea","tid":2163531,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b460cad17ac070a1d2abf421a2f22986a7839155","tid":2163531,"uid":322711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"咩死法會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n <br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5rXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=497f06fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"53d9784f45c0c50694ae053b82a8c7a85baeb20b","tid":2163531,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaefefb37984be2b0e1a2a52be7817124440a4f9","tid":2163531,"uid":322711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e053529f73b437e788938e6293dab9a5389abbde","tid":2163531,"uid":126534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5b194de43be5b89d62b04e84788c8e4795c222b","tid":2163531,"uid":321161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:22:40.000Z","msg":"講出黎會舒服d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"人多好辦事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"無人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T18:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5356732f9c0bedcf7b610d137ff6fa3cbce963a3","tid":2163531,"uid":128120,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b460cad17ac070a1d2abf421a2f22986a7839155","tid":2163531,"uid":322711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:16:22.000Z","msg":"咩死法會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"起完底發現絲打你好負能量<br />\n有需要搵人傾傾可以搵我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw你男朋友黎唔到己成事實<br />\n仲有一班手足聽日會黎聽審<br />\n我地唔會放棄你<br />\n會等到你出黎為止<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"852c1bd79fa93a22149b6b85ad85dd70f4c29102","tid":2163531,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"}]}